<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Classement Économique — Amérique du Nord · Europe · Océanie</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{--bg:#07090d;--s1:#0c1018;--s2:#111620;--s3:#161d2a;--b1:#1a2235;--b2:#243048;--gold:#c9a84c;--gold2:#e8c96a;--gold-dim:#7a5e28;--teal:#22d4d4;--rose:#e05c6a;--green:#3ecf8e;--amber:#e8a020;--blue:#4a9eff;--violet:#9b7eff;--text:#dce8f5;--dim:#6e899e;--muted:#2f4559;--us:#4a9eff;--ca:#ff7878;--eu:#9b7eff;--au:#3ecf8e}
*,*::before,*::after{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden}
body::before{content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(var(--b1) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,var(--b1) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:56px 56px;opacity:.22;pointer-events:none;z-index:0}
.wrap{position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1600px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 28px 72px}
/* HEADER */
header{padding:52px 0 36px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--b1);margin-bottom:28px}
.eyebrow{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px}
.eyebrow::before{content:'';display:block;width:28px;height:1px;background:var(--gold)}
h1{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(30px,4.5vw,64px);font-weight:900;line-height:1.02;letter-spacing:-2px;color:var(--text)}
h1 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--gold)}
.header-desc{margin-top:14px;font-size:11px;color:var(--dim);line-height:1.9;max-width:660px;letter-spacing:.4px}
.header-meta{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:16px}
.meta-pill{font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:.8px;border:1px solid var(--b1);border-radius:3px;padding:4px 10px}
.meta-pill span{color:var(--dim)}
.ppa-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:5px 14px;background:rgba(201,168,76,.1);border:1px solid var(--gold-dim);border-radius:3px;font-size:10px;color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:1px;margin-top:12px}
/* CONTROLS */
.controls{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:14px;margin-bottom:18px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.region-group{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px}
.region-label{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted)}
.region-toggles{display:flex;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.rtog{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:9px 16px;border-radius:4px;border:1px solid var(--b2);background:var(--s1);color:var(--dim);font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:1px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .18s;white-space:nowrap}
.rtog:hover:not(.active){color:var(--text);background:var(--s2)}
.rtog.active[data-r="us"]{background:rgba(74,158,255,.12);color:var(--us);border-color:var(--us)}
.rtog.active[data-r="ca"]{background:rgba(255,120,120,.12);color:var(--ca);border-color:var(--ca)}
.rtog.active[data-r="eu"]{background:rgba(155,126,255,.12);color:var(--eu);border-color:var(--eu)}
.rtog.active[data-r="au"]{background:rgba(62,207,142,.12);color:var(--au);border-color:var(--au)}
.rtog-dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0}
.rtog.active[data-r="us"] .rtog-dot{background:var(--us)}
.rtog.active[data-r="ca"] .rtog-dot{background:var(--ca)}
.rtog.active[data-r="eu"] .rtog-dot{background:var(--eu)}
.rtog.active[data-r="au"] .rtog-dot{background:var(--au)}
.rtog:not(.active) .rtog-dot{background:var(--muted)}
.rtog-count{margin-left:4px;padding:1px 6px;background:var(--bg);border-radius:10px;font-size:9px;opacity:.7}
.ctrl-right{margin-left:auto;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.search-wrap{position:relative}
.search-wrap input{width:230px;padding:9px 14px 9px 34px;background:var(--s1);border:1px solid var(--b2);border-radius:4px;color:var(--text);font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.8px;outline:none;transition:border-color .2s}
.search-wrap input::placeholder{color:var(--muted)}
.search-wrap input:focus{border-color:var(--gold-dim)}
.search-wrap::before{content:'⌕';position:absolute;left:11px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);color:var(--dim);font-size:15px;pointer-events:none}
.col-toggle-btn{padding:9px 16px;background:var(--s1);border:1px solid var(--b2);border-radius:4px;color:var(--dim);font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;cursor:pointer;transition:all .18s;white-space:nowrap}
.col-toggle-btn:hover{color:var(--text);background:var(--s2)}
.col-toggle-btn.open{color:var(--gold);border-color:var(--gold-dim)}
.col-panel{position:absolute;top:calc(100% + 8px);right:0;background:var(--s2);border:1px solid var(--b2);border-radius:6px;padding:16px;z-index:100;min-width:340px;display:none;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;box-shadow:0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,.6)}
.col-panel.open{display:flex}
.col-panel-title{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:6px}
.col-groups{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:4px}
.col-check{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:7px 10px;border-radius:3px;cursor:pointer;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.8px;color:var(--dim);transition:background .15s;user-select:none}
.col-check:hover{background:var(--s3);color:var(--text)}
.col-check input[type=checkbox]{accent-color:var(--gold);cursor:pointer}
.col-check.checked{color:var(--text)}
.col-panel-actions{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:6px;border-top:1px solid var(--b1);padding-top:10px}
.col-action-btn{padding:5px 12px;font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;border:1px solid var(--b2);background:transparent;color:var(--dim);transition:all .15s}
.col-action-btn:hover{color:var(--text);background:var(--s3)}
/* SORT BAR */
.sort-bar{display:flex;gap:5px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:18px;align-items:center}
.sort-label{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-right:4px}
.sbtn{padding:6px 12px;background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--b1);border-radius:3px;color:var(--muted);font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;white-space:nowrap}
.sbtn:hover{color:var(--dim);border-color:var(--b2)}
.sbtn.active{background:var(--gold);color:var(--bg);border-color:var(--gold);font-weight:600}
/* STATS STRIP */
.stats-strip{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(140px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--b1);border:1px solid var(--b1);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:20px}
.sc{background:var(--s1);padding:18px 18px 14px;transition:background .2s}
.sc:hover{background:var(--s2)}
.sc-label{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:6px}
.sc-val{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold);line-height:1}
.sc-sub{font-size:10px;color:var(--dim);margin-top:3px}
/* TABLE */
.table-outer{border:1px solid var(--b1);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;position:relative}
.table-outer::after{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;width:50px;background:linear-gradient(to right,transparent,var(--bg));pointer-events:none;z-index:10;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0}
.table-scroll{overflow-x:auto;overflow-y:visible}
.table-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar{height:7px}
.table-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:var(--s1)}
.table-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--b2);border-radius:4px}
table{width:max-content;min-width:100%;border-collapse:collapse}
/* sticky */
th:nth-child(1),td:nth-child(1){position:sticky;left:0;z-index:3;background:var(--s2)}
th:nth-child(2),td:nth-child(2){position:sticky;left:52px;z-index:3;background:var(--s2)}
thead th:nth-child(1),thead th:nth-child(2){background:var(--s3);z-index:4}
tbody tr:hover td:nth-child(1),tbody tr:hover td:nth-child(2){background:var(--s3)}
/* TH */
thead{background:var(--s3)}
th{padding:12px 14px;text-align:left;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);border-bottom:1px solid var(--b1);white-space:nowrap;cursor:pointer;user-select:none;transition:color .2s;background:var(--s3)}
th:hover{color:var(--gold)}
th.sorted{color:var(--gold)}
th:first-child{width:50px;cursor:default;text-align:center}
th:nth-child(2){min-width:200px;cursor:default}
th .si{margin-left:5px;opacity:.4;font-size:10px}
th.sorted .si{opacity:1}
/* source badge in th */
.src-tag{display:inline-block;font-size:7px;letter-spacing:.8px;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:2px;background:var(--b2);color:var(--muted);margin-left:4px;vertical-align:middle;font-weight:500}
/* TD */
tbody tr{border-bottom:1px solid var(--b1);transition:background .12s;animation:rIn .22s ease both}
tbody tr:last-child{border-bottom:none}
tbody tr:hover{background:var(--s2)}
@keyframes rIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(3px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}
td{padding:11px 14px;font-size:12px;vertical-align:middle;background:var(--s1)}
tbody tr:hover td{background:var(--s2)}
.rk{text-align:center;font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:var(--muted)}
tbody tr:nth-child(1) .rk{color:var(--gold);font-size:17px}
tbody tr:nth-child(2) .rk{color:#a0b4c8;font-size:15px}
tbody tr:nth-child(3) .rk{color:#8a7060}
.nc{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px}
.flag{font-size:18px;flex-shrink:0}
.n1{font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);letter-spacing:.2px}
.n2{font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:1px;letter-spacing:.4px}
.rdot{width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;margin-left:auto}
.rdot-us{background:var(--us)}.rdot-ca{background:var(--ca)}.rdot-eu{background:var(--eu)}.rdot-au{background:var(--au)}
.dc{position:relative;min-width:110px;padding-bottom:16px!important}
.dc .vn{font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums}
.dc .vs{font-size:9px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2px;letter-spacing:.4px}
.bt{position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:var(--b1)}
.bf{height:100%;border-radius:0 2px 2px 0;transition:width .5s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1)}
.badge{display:inline-block;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:2px;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums}
.gini-lo{background:rgba(62,207,142,.13);color:var(--green)}.gini-md{background:rgba(232,160,32,.13);color:var(--amber)}.gini-hi{background:rgba(224,92,106,.13);color:var(--rose)}
.life-hi{background:rgba(62,207,142,.13);color:var(--green)}.life-md{background:rgba(201,168,76,.13);color:var(--gold)}.life-lo{background:rgba(224,92,106,.13);color:var(--rose)}
.hdi-hi{background:rgba(62,207,142,.13);color:var(--green)}.hdi-md{background:rgba(201,168,76,.13);color:var(--gold)}.hdi-lo{background:rgba(224,92,106,.13);color:var(--rose)}
/* SOURCE TAGS */
.region-src{display:flex;gap:10px;margin-bottom:12px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.src-chip{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.8px;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:3px;border:1px solid var(--b1);color:var(--dim)}
.src-chip strong{color:var(--text)}
/* LEGEND */
.legend{display:flex;gap:20px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:14px}
.li{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;font-size:10px;color:var(--muted)}
.ldot{width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:50%}
/* NOTES */
.notes{margin-top:28px;padding:20px 24px;background:var(--s1);border:1px solid var(--b1);border-radius:6px;border-left:3px solid var(--gold-dim)}
.notes-t{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:12px}
.notes-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px}
@media(max-width:768px){.notes-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
.notes-col h4{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--teal);margin-bottom:8px}
.notes p{font-size:10px;color:var(--dim);line-height:1.9;margin-bottom:6px}
.notes p strong{color:var(--text)}
.notes p:last-child{margin-bottom:0}
/* scroll hint */
.scroll-hint{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:8px}
.scroll-hint span{animation:nudge 2s ease-in-out infinite}
@keyframes nudge{0%,100%{transform:translateX(0)}50%{transform:translateX(4px)}}
.no-results{text-align:center;padding:48px 20px;font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:1px}
.ctrl-wrapper{position:relative}
[data-tip]:hover::after{content:attr(data-tip);position:absolute;bottom:calc(100% + 7px);left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);background:var(--s3);border:1px solid var(--b2);color:var(--text);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.4px;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:3px;white-space:nowrap;z-index:200;pointer-events:none}
@media(max-width:768px){.wrap{padding:0 14px 48px}.ctrl-right{margin-left:0}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

<header>
  <div class="eyebrow">Analyse comparative · Monde occidental</div>
  <h1>Classement <em>Économique</em><br>& Qualité de Vie</h1>
  <p class="header-desc">
    États américains, provinces canadiennes, pays européens et régions australasiennes —
    comparés selon le PIB, la distribution des richesses, le bien-être social, l'éducation et l'environnement.
    Toutes les valeurs monétaires sont en <strong>Dollars Internationaux PPA 2024</strong>.
  </p>
  <div class="header-meta">
    <div class="meta-pill">Référence GDP/USA · <span>BEA, données 2024</span></div>
    <div class="meta-pill">Canada · <span>StatsCan Tableau 36-10-0222-01, 2024</span></div>
    <div class="meta-pill">Europe · <span>FMI WEO / Banque Mondiale, 2024</span></div>
    <div class="meta-pill">Australie · <span>ABS Comptes Nationaux, 2023-24</span></div>
    <div class="meta-pill">N.-Z. · <span>Stats NZ / FMI PPA 2024</span></div>
  </div>
  <div class="ppa-badge">🔄 Parité de Pouvoir d'Achat — Dollars Internationaux 2024 · Référence = USD</div>
</header>

<div class="controls">
  <div class="region-group">
    <div class="region-label">Régions actives (multi-sélection)</div>
    <div class="region-toggles">
      <button class="rtog active" data-r="us" onclick="toggleRegion('us')">
        <div class="rtog-dot"></div>🇺🇸 États-Unis<span class="rtog-count" id="cnt-us">50</span>
      </button>
      <button class="rtog active" data-r="ca" onclick="toggleRegion('ca')">
        <div class="rtog-dot"></div>🇨🇦 Canada<span class="rtog-count" id="cnt-ca">13</span>
      </button>
      <button class="rtog active" data-r="eu" onclick="toggleRegion('eu')">
        <div class="rtog-dot"></div>🌍 Europe<span class="rtog-count" id="cnt-eu">20</span>
      </button>
      <button class="rtog active" data-r="au" onclick="toggleRegion('au')">
        <div class="rtog-dot"></div>🌏 Australasie<span class="rtog-count" id="cnt-au">9</span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="ctrl-right">
    <div class="search-wrap">
      <input type="text" id="searchInput" placeholder="Rechercher une région…" oninput="renderTable()">
    </div>
    <div class="ctrl-wrapper">
      <button class="col-toggle-btn" id="colBtn" onclick="toggleColPanel()">⊞ Colonnes</button>
      <div class="col-panel" id="colPanel">
        <div class="col-panel-title">Choisir les colonnes</div>
        <div class="col-groups" id="colChecks"></div>
        <div class="col-panel-actions">
          <button class="col-action-btn" onclick="setAllCols(true)">Tout afficher</button>
          <button class="col-action-btn" onclick="setAllCols(false)">Tout masquer</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="sort-bar">
  <span class="sort-label">Trier par :</span>
  <button class="sbtn active" data-k="gdp"      onclick="quickSort(this,'gdp')"     >PIB</button>
  <button class="sbtn"        data-k="gdppc"    onclick="quickSort(this,'gdppc')"   >PIB/hab.</button>
  <button class="sbtn"        data-k="gini"     onclick="quickSort(this,'gini')"    >Gini</button>
  <button class="sbtn"        data-k="median"   onclick="quickSort(this,'median')"  >Rev. médian</button>
  <button class="sbtn"        data-k="poverty"  onclick="quickSort(this,'poverty')" >Pauvreté</button>
  <button class="sbtn"        data-k="life"     onclick="quickSort(this,'life')"    >Espér. vie</button>
  <button class="sbtn"        data-k="hdi"      onclick="quickSort(this,'hdi')"     >IDH</button>
  <button class="sbtn"        data-k="health"   onclick="quickSort(this,'health')"  >Santé/hab.</button>
  <button class="sbtn"        data-k="homicide" onclick="quickSort(this,'homicide')">Homicides</button>
  <button class="sbtn"        data-k="top10"    onclick="quickSort(this,'top10')"   >Top 10%</button>
  <button class="sbtn"        data-k="mob"      onclick="quickSort(this,'mob')"     >Mobilité</button>
  <button class="sbtn"        data-k="edu"      onclick="quickSort(this,'edu')"     >Éducation</button>
  <button class="sbtn"        data-k="co2"      onclick="quickSort(this,'co2')"     >CO₂/hab.</button>
  <button class="sbtn"        data-k="unemp"    onclick="quickSort(this,'unemp')"   >Chômage</button>
</div>

<div class="stats-strip" id="statsStrip"></div>

<div class="scroll-hint"><span>→</span> Défilement horizontal pour toutes les colonnes · colonnes Rang & Région fixes</div>

<div class="table-outer">
  <div class="table-scroll">
    <table id="mainTable">
      <thead><tr id="theadRow"></tr></thead>
      <tbody id="tbody"></tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="legend">
  <div class="li"><div class="ldot" style="background:var(--green)"></div>Favorable</div>
  <div class="li"><div class="ldot" style="background:var(--amber)"></div>Intermédiaire</div>
  <div class="li"><div class="ldot" style="background:var(--rose)"></div>Défavorable</div>
  <div class="li"><div class="ldot" style="background:var(--us)"></div>🇺🇸 BEA 2024</div>
  <div class="li"><div class="ldot" style="background:var(--ca)"></div>🇨🇦 StatsCan 2024 (PPA)</div>
  <div class="li"><div class="ldot" style="background:var(--eu)"></div>🌍 FMI/BM 2024 (PPA)</div>
  <div class="li"><div class="ldot" style="background:var(--au)"></div>🌏 ABS 2023-24 (PPA)</div>
</div>

<div class="notes">
  <div class="notes-t">Sources & Méthodologie</div>
  <div class="notes-grid">
    <div class="notes-col">
      <h4>Hiérarchie des Sources GDP</h4>
      <p><strong>🇺🇸 États-Unis :</strong> BEA (Bureau of Economic Analysis), GDP par État 2024, dollars courants nominaux. Le dollar américain étant la monnaie de référence PPA, aucune conversion n'est nécessaire.</p>
      <p><strong>🇨🇦 Canada :</strong> Statistique Canada, Tableau 36-10-0222-01, PIB nominal 2024 en CAD. Converti en Dollars Internationaux via le taux PPA implicite du FMI 2024 (1 $CA ≈ 0,862 $Int'l). Note : même facteur pour toutes les provinces — sous-estime les régions à coût élevé, surestime les régions à coût bas.</p>
      <p><strong>🌍 Europe :</strong> FMI World Economic Outlook (WEO) / Banque Mondiale 2024, GDP PPA en dollars internationaux courants. L'Irlande est fortement distordue par les activités des multinationales (PIB/hab. effectif ≈ 60-65 k$).</p>
      <p><strong>🌏 Australie :</strong> ABS, Comptes Nationaux des États (State Accounts), année fiscale 2023-24, parts du GSP national converties en $Int'l (1 $AUD ≈ 0,722 $Int'l PPA 2024). <strong>Nouvelle-Zélande :</strong> Stats NZ / FMI PPA 2024.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="notes-col">
      <h4>Normalisation Monétaire</h4>
      <p><strong>Dollars Internationaux (PPA) :</strong> Monnaie hypothétique ayant le même pouvoir d'achat que le dollar américain aux États-Unis. Permet des comparaisons réelles inter-régionales indépendamment des taux de change.</p>
      <p><strong>Taux PPA utilisés (2024) :</strong> CAD → ×0,862 · AUD → ×0,722 · NZD → ×0,680. Les valeurs européennes (FMI) sont déjà exprimées en dollars internationaux.</p>
